        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1495568" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16670616931317726116">&quot;The Secret Sharer&quot; is one of my favorite stories. It takes place on a ship on the ocean, but it&apos;s also as if it takes place in the subconscious mind. It&apos;s dreamy. I loved it.</span>
  <span id="freeText16670616931317726116" style="display:none">"The Secret Sharer" is one of my favorite stories. It takes place on a ship on the ocean, but it's also as if it takes place in the subconscious mind. It's dreamy. I loved it.</span>
