        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer34062026" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8338656216981213118">There&apos;s something vaguely magical about Conrad&apos;s ships. The Secret Sharer is definitely the best, but Youth: A Narrative is pretty decent. Typhoon was a tad boring, though. The Captain wasn&apos;t dynamic or interesting and some of the ship descriptions were perhaps too technical for modern readers.</span>
  <span id="freeText8338656216981213118" style="display:none">There's something vaguely magical about Conrad's ships. The Secret Sharer is definitely the best, but Youth: A Narrative is pretty decent. Typhoon was a tad boring, though. The Captain wasn't dynamic or interesting and some of the ship descriptions were perhaps too technical for modern readers.</span>
