<span id="freeTextContainer9321299160459587921">Conrad and I simply never clicked. I never really like his over use of description and attempts at suspense. This book is one of the few with the doppelganger motif and he leaves things rather vague in this respect, and put bluntly, it seemed rather a story about nothing much.</span>

          </span>
